    "en": {
      "title": "Announcement regarding bus fare revision today",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The final decision on the bus fare revision, which will take effect from July 1, will be announced on Tuesday (28).",
        "Dr. Nilan Mirunda, Director General of the National Transport Commission, said the idea should be put forward to provide fuel on relief basis to private bus owners without increasing bus fares in line with fuel prices.",
        "The bus fare revision will be revised on the first of July every year.",
        "The National Transport Commission is looking at revising bus fares for 12 ideas.",
        "The Private Bus Owners' Association has demanded that bus fares be revised due to fuel shortages and rising fuel prices.",
        "The final decision will be announced following crucial discussions with the Ministry of Transport today regarding the bus fare revision.",
        "If the bus fare is increased in view of the increase in fuel prices then the general public will be affected.",
        "He said the idea put forward on the basis of fuel relief in the short term for private bus owners without increasing bus fares at the present stage would be considered."
      ],
